{"nodes":[{"pos":[12,49],"content":"Compiler Error C3044 | Microsoft Docs","needQuote":false,"needEscape":true,"nodes":[{"content":"Compiler Error C3044 | Microsoft Docs","pos":[0,37]}]},{"content":"Compiler Error C3044","pos":[618,638]},{"content":"'section' : only allowed directly nested under an OpenMP 'sections' directive","pos":[639,716]},{"content":"The compiler found a <ph id=\"ph1\">`section`</ph> directive was used incorrectly.","pos":[723,785],"source":"The compiler found a `section` directive was used incorrectly."},{"content":"For more information, see <bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt>sections<ept id=\"p1\">](../../parallel/openmp/reference/sections-openmp.md)</ept>.","pos":[786,875],"source":" For more information, see [sections](../../parallel/openmp/reference/sections-openmp.md)."},{"content":"The following sample generates C3044:","pos":[882,919]}],"content":"---\ntitle: \"Compiler Error C3044 | Microsoft Docs\"\nms.custom: \"\"\nms.date: \"11/04/2016\"\nms.reviewer: \"\"\nms.suite: \"\"\nms.technology: \n  - \"devlang-csharp\"\nms.tgt_pltfrm: \"\"\nms.topic: \"article\"\nf1_keywords: \n  - \"C3044\"\ndev_langs: \n  - \"C++\"\nhelpviewer_keywords: \n  - \"C3044\"\nms.assetid: 9f3e25b2-4676-49ab-97bf-6c88cd0fa377\ncaps.latest.revision: 8\nauthor: \"corob-msft\"\nms.author: \"corob\"\nmanager: \"ghogen\"\ntranslation.priority.ht: \n  - \"de-de\"\n  - \"es-es\"\n  - \"fr-fr\"\n  - \"it-it\"\n  - \"ja-jp\"\n  - \"ko-kr\"\n  - \"ru-ru\"\n  - \"zh-cn\"\n  - \"zh-tw\"\ntranslation.priority.mt: \n  - \"cs-cz\"\n  - \"pl-pl\"\n  - \"pt-br\"\n  - \"tr-tr\"\n---\n# Compiler Error C3044\n'section' : only allowed directly nested under an OpenMP 'sections' directive  \n  \n The compiler found a `section` directive was used incorrectly. For more information, see [sections](../../parallel/openmp/reference/sections-openmp.md).  \n  \n The following sample generates C3044:  \n  \n```  \n// C3044.cpp  \n// compile with: /openmp /c  \n#include \"omp.h\"  \nint main() {  \n   int n2 = 2, n3 = 3;  \n  \n   #pragma omp parallel  \n   {  \n      ++n2;  \n  \n      #pragma omp sections  \n      {  \n         ++n2;  \n      }  \n  \n      #pragma omp section   // C3044  \n      {  \n         ++n3;  \n      }  \n   }  \n  \n   #pragma omp parallel  \n   {  \n      ++n2;  \n  \n      #pragma omp sections  \n      {  \n         #pragma omp section   // OK  \n         {  \n            ++n3;  \n         }  \n      }  \n   }  \n}  \n```"}